title: Pre-Leasing Studio Apartment!!!
posting_body: ['WELCOME TO TL RESIDENCES', 'Beautiful Studio With Amazing Community Spaces', 'Find Home in the heart of the Tenderloin in San Francisco, a neighborhood with a rich and colorful history and an exciting mix of notable venues that lend to the area’s reputation as a thriving entertainment district.', 'At TL Residences, you’ll discover a stunning selection of modern studio apartments that are rich with contemporary features, offering a contrast from the classic feel of the neighborhood.', 'Breathtaking city views, beautiful interior finishes, and tech-forward features like smart access and smart outlets await you in these efficiently designed residences that showcase the globally inspired trend of scaled living.', 'Community Features:', '•\tLevel 2 Courtyard & Lounge', '•\tCommunity Space w/ Kitchen', '•\tYoga Studio', '•\tGathering Area w/ Fireplace', '•\tCommunal Alley Garden', '•\tPackage Room w/ Cold Storage', '•\tConcierge', '•\tArrival Lounge w/ Mail Center', '•\tNon-Smoking Community', '•\tInduction Cooktop', '•\tBBQ & Bar Area', '•\tMovie Theater Lounge', '•\tMonthly Resident Events', '•\tLobby w/ Beverage Experience Center', '•\tCommunity Laundry Center', '•\tRooftop Lounge w/ Firepits', '•\tCommunity Fitness Gym', 'Apartment Features:', '•\tPre-Installed Mounted Flat Screen TV', '•\tFiltered Air System', '•\tSmart Access Apartments', '•\tBuilt-In Murphy Beds*', '•\tMobile Wardrobe', '•\tVinyl Flooring w/ Hardwood Finish', '•\tStep-In Shower', '•\tSmart Outlets', 'Office Hours', 'Monday – Friday 9am-6pm', 'Saturday and Sunday 10am-5pm', "Don't miss this opportunity.", 'For more information about this property, please Contact Us at', 'show contact info', 'or Apply Online at San Francisco Apartments | TL Residences <URL>)', 'TL Residences - BRAND NEW LUXURY STUDIOS', '361 Turk Street', 'San Francisco, CA 94102']
